      "id": "9fbb2ae4a9b5615c",
      "text": "If you do not already have an SSH key pair, which consists of a public and private key, you need to generate one. If you already have a key that you want to use, skip to the Copy SSH Keys to Server step."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "319d34cf9c8cf472",
